<s> There may be an editorial typo in the specification of the one-argument base-uri.  </s>
<s> The result is that it is unclear where the base-uri of a text node be non-empty.  </s>
<s> I think the intent is "yes", in which case I think this one-word fix will help.  </s>
<s> Change  </s>
<s> "The base-uri of all other node types is the empty sequence."  </s>
<s> to "The base-uri property of all other node types is the empty sequence."  </s>
<s> From the context, that appears to have been the intent.  </s>
<s> Both the Functions and Operators and the Data Model documents have the same problem.  </s>
